Package com.blahti.drag

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DragListener
    Interface to receive notifications when a drag starts or stops
    DragSource
    Interface defining an object where drag operations originate.
    DropTarget
    Interface defining an object that can receive a view at the end of a drag operation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DragController
    This class is used to initiate a drag within a view or across multiple views.
    DragLayer
    A ViewGroup that coordinates dragging across its descendants.
    DragView
    A DragView is a special view used by a DragController.
    MyAbsoluteLayout
    A layout that lets you specify exact locations (x/y coordinates) of its children.
    MyAbsoluteLayout.LayoutParams
    Per-child layout information associated with MyAbsoluteLayout.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DragController.DragBehavior
